data.description: Beautifully remodeled and upgraded Two-Story home ready to impress.  You are welcomed with a double-door entrance, soaring vaulted ceiling, the hallmark of a beautiful Sunnymead home, and the elegance of a sweeping staircase that takes you to the 3 upstairs bedrooms of good sizes. This home has a downstairs bedroom with a large bathroom next to the indoor Laundry room. This 4 bedroom, 3 bath features new interior paint and flooring, and an open, updated kitchen with breakfast nook. High ceilings, large windows and recessed lighting make the home light, bright and beautiful. Bathrooms are updated, with a primary bath featuring double sinks, separate tub, and walk-in shower. This high-tech home includes smart appliances, ring doorbell and smart nest thermostat. The 2-car garage has updated epoxy floors, and a side mount garage motor. The true gem is the backyard! Large lot with mountain views is perfect for gatherings of family or friends. Conveniently located close to Schools, shopping, dining, freeway access, hiking, biking and horse trails, Sunnymead Ranch Community also offers access to the Lake Club, pool, spa, parks and more!
